# ── Ghost journal (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Point these at any Ghost blog and the Field Journal section switches from
# the local entries in src/data/journal.ts to live posts.
# Content API keys are read-only and safe to expose in a static site.
# Ghost admin → Settings → Integrations → Add custom integration → Content API key
#VITE_GHOST_URL=https://zink.ghost.io
#VITE_GHOST_KEY=22444f78447824223cefc48062
#VITE_GHOST_TAG=journal

# ── PathCompanion live sync (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────
# Once the character endpoint is known (run `npm run sync`, or check
# DevTools → Network while viewing the sheet), set it here and the deployed
# site re-fetches the sheet on every visit. {key} {account} {character}
# are replaced automatically.
#VITE_PC_API=https://pathcompanion.com/api/character?key={key}

# Override the baked-in character key without touching code:
#PATHCOMPANION_KEY=eyJhY2NvdW50IjoiMjdDN0IzRjY0RkQ4NTU5MiIsImNoYXJhY3RlciI6ImNoYXJhY3RlcjEzIn0=
